edu.brown.cs.ivy.jcomp

Class JcompSymbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.ivy.jcomp.JcompSymbol

  • public abstract class JcompSymbol
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a resolved symbol. All definitions and uses of the symbol will refer to the same symbol object. Methods provide information about the symbol.
